rComments: Heather was one of the best profs I ever had. Very passionate about the subject, truly cares about her students and tries to help whenever possible. She would always time time ti explain new concepts and make sure EVERYONE gets them. We had quizzes almost every class, but I found that it helped me stay on top of things.

She will try her best to ensure you succeed, as long as you do attend the lectures and do the homework. The quiz and assignments were easy and based on the homework questions. She responds very fast to emails and is active on twitter.

rComments: Teacher uses powerpoints but relays info to real life examples. In class problems are a huge help. She offers extra help but also expects you to be prepared.

Be weary of taking this class with her!Tells you one thing to study for,test ends up covering what she said won't be on there. Only teaches from powerpoint slides, but does offer extra help. Doesnt try to make sure students understand in her lectures as she's only reading from slides. Not really responsive outside of class to students' need of help
